Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.71,0:07:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\frz8.604\pos(515.999,979.001)\fs40}遇見她，是在春天。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.57,0:08:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,這就哭啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.08,0:08:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,要當一輩子朋友哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.93,0:08:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  安曇
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.71,0:08:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,安曇  再靠近點嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.17,0:08:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,那就拍囉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.48,0:08:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你們倆表情都好僵硬啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.60,0:08:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,那我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.66,0:08:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.40,0:08:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你個死現充
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.91,0:08:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,好醜啊  小太
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.48,0:08:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.31,0:08:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,都死魚眼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.53,0:08:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,畢竟寫了一通宵嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.04,0:08:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,重新執筆了嗎  老師
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.62,0:08:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.42,0:08:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼故事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.25,0:08:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.20,0:08:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,哦？看樣子是小黃書啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.20,0:08:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,黃太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.31,0:08:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,才不是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.17,0:08:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,欸  我想看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.64,0:08:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,不給不給不給不給
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.57,0:09:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,好不容易寫一次
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.22,0:09:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,傳到投稿網站嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.22,0:09:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.37,0:09:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,水野
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.93,0:09:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,上了高中要繼續哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.73,0:09:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  比良也是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.86,0:09:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,賽場再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.71,0:09:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.53,0:10:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,小茜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.08,0:10:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.42,0:10:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,讓你久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.24,0:10:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,沒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.36,0:10:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,搬家準備辛苦嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.93,0:10:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我家已經習慣了的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.53,0:10:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,明天是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.77,0:10:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.95,0:10:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,下次什麼時候能見面？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.64,0:10:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,隨時都可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.84,0:10:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我能去找你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.13,0:10:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.97,0:10:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我每週都會去的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.84,0:10:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.57,0:10:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  不方便嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.22,0:10:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.42,0:11:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,電車費很貴的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.60,0:11:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我會打工的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.71,0:11:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我也打工
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.82,0:11:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,田徑部怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.42,0:11:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我也想繼續……
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.93,0:11:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我去找你好了  放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.13,0:11:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,每週打三次工  電車費還是賺得到的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.65,0:11:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.86,0:11:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,單程要兩小時嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.75,0:11:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.57,0:11:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我坐始發車過去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.68,0:11:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,欸？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.65,0:11:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,能多在一起一點時間
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.55,0:11:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,還是跟以前一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.37,0:11:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,而且還有LINE
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.22,0:11:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,可是……
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.04,0:11:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,只讓小太郎一個人受苦……
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.95,0:11:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.48,0:11:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我也有存款的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.55,0:11:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,真不用勉強的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.68,0:11:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.01,0:11:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,欸？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.95,0:11:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,小茜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.44,0:11:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我想問你點事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.00,0:11:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.24,0:12:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,被告白了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.74,0:12:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我聽千夏說了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.58,0:12:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,確實被告白了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.00,0:12:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼……
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.73,0:12:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,欸？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.67,0:12:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼不告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.80,0:12:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,因為……我已經拒絕了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.17,0:12:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,通常情況下不說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.26,0:12:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我會擔心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.93,0:12:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,欸？怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.75,0:12:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.26,0:13:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.48,0:13:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我……
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.80,0:13:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,一直……不安
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.46,0:13:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,很不安
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.53,0:13:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,總是給小太郎添麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.26,0:13:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,這最令我痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.04,0:13:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我該怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.51,0:15:33.16,Notes,,0,0,0,,（孩子她媽  這個能扔了嗎）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.16,0:15:34.49,Notes,,0,0,0,,（這個是哪個啊）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.57,0:15:36.53,Notes,,0,0,0,,（可別給搬家公司搗亂哦）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.68,0:15:39.20,Notes,,0,0,0,,（媽媽  搬家公司的人叫你呢）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.46,0:15:41.08,Notes,,0,0,0,,（喊你爸去）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.51,0:16:01.08,Notes,,0,0,0,,（小茜  沒忘東西吧）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.66,0:16:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,沒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.88,0:16:27.60,Notes,,0,0,0,,（這是最後一箱了）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.60,0:16:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,-不好  鼻子好酸啊  -謝謝你們
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.08,0:16:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,要寂寞了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.44,0:16:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你又來了  別說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.64,0:16:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,等等  喂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.15,0:16:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.84,0:16:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.60,0:16:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.40,0:16:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,小茜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.57,0:16:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,小茜要晚點坐電車來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.75,0:16:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,欸？可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.51,0:16:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,朋友都跑來送你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.75,0:17:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你也想慢慢聊會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.75,0:17:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.84,0:17:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,吶  小茜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.08,0:17:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,安曇呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.55,0:17:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  那個
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.60,0:17:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  對了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.77,0:17:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你等等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.01,0:17:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,看這個
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.97,0:17:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.84,0:17:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\frz4.969\pos(969.6,892.2)\fs47}如果真的存在命運之神，那他一定很喜歡捉弄人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.48,0:17:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\frz3.867\pos(340.8,412.2)\fs47}她是田徑部的100公尺選手。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.48,0:17:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\frz3.867\pos(748.8,721.8)\fs47}在她刷新最佳個人成績時，我像為自己慶祝似的由衷地感到開心。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.51,0:17:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\frz4.043\pos(681.6,388.2)\fs47}我是文藝部的部長，一邊注視著她奔跑的身姿一邊下筆。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.51,0:17:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\frz4.043\pos(518.4,729)\fs47}雖然作品沒能問世，不過你誇它很棒。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.93,0:17:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\frz4.043\pos(609.6,438.6)\fs47}在神社第一次見面那天，我緊張得說不出話。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.00,0:17:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,寫的是我和……小太郎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.73,0:18:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,小太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.60,0:18:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,是今天吧  搬家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.24,0:18:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.68,0:18:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,話說  我看過你寫的網路小說了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.90,0:18:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,那個……
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.02,0:19:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,都更新了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.06,0:19:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.44,0:19:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,評論不少啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.95,0:19:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,欸？
